gw.api.database.upgrade

Class DatamodelChangeWithoutDatabaseChange<D extends VersionAction>

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.database.upgrade.DatamodelChangeWithoutDatabaseChange<D>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDatamodelChange<D>

    public final class DatamodelChangeWithoutDatabaseChange<D extends VersionAction>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDatamodelChange<D>
    IDatamodelChange that changes only the archived document but not the database. Essentially, it wraps the given VersionTrigger in an IDatamodelChange that returns null for the database Version Trigger.
